                            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Arsenal Vault Desktop stores all your data locally on your computer — it never leaves your machine. Your vault is encrypted with AES-256. Even if someone accessed your computer, they couldn't read your inventory without your password. <a href="../security.html" class="text-av-gold hover:underline">Read the security overview.</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
